:46:29.000Z","msg":"啲人成日話有槍嘅話香港獨立咗<br />\n但係事實係擺支槍喺你面前 <br />\n你同我都唔敢開槍殺狗<br />\n與其話香港人缺乏武器 <br />\n其實香港人真正缺乏嘅喺革命意識<br />\n佢地雖然口港光復香港 <br />\n但係實情係佢地都知獨立係無可能嘅事<br />\n我認為香港要有大部分人有做叛賊竊國嘅決心<br />\n先有資格諗武器從何來<br />\n所以暫時現階段 我認為長時間嘅文宣係比勇武緊要"},{"pid":"07f1556b6f3371ff60e4bc6ff756452acbfd9eb7","tid":2000462,"uid":38777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T00:59:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d876b7bf06d54fdbe81c10fc72c5b67bf4a364f","tid":2000462,"uid":34594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T01:10:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"42e6b11e2640519571d294158617292ebe337ef8","tid":2000462,"uid":238660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T01:19:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"83454d234d944c1e5fc6b8b17f6b58547c193dbc","tid":2000462,"uid":135124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T01:21:27.000Z","msg":"學術野 考完試睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8de154f603e5544b28111822290d4e27f9443447","tid":2000462,"uid":238660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"83454d234d944c1e5fc6b8b17f6b58547c193dbc","tid":2000462,"uid":135124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T01:21:27.000Z","msg":"學術野 考完試睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T01:28:43.000Z","msg":"手足 加油"},{"pid":"5c48129bbcac8724bfaa3dfc98ff6ff09ce8912a","tid":2000462,"uid":285204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T01:41:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cf1d9409c6025294d105c049f00e9de40d9a43b6","tid":2000462,"uid":62807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T04:53:58.000Z","msg":"本來都想睇呢本書<br />\n感謝整理"},{"pid":"8695acc7ea775b6bd7bea3b86ca37f1d2493afdf","tid":